      "content": "i've tried all that. the therapists, the talking... it doesn't change the fact that i'm still me, and i'm still the one causing them stress. it feels like i'm just running in circles while they suffer. help doesn't fix the reality that my presence is the variable that makes everything harder. doesn't it just seem more logical that the easiest way to fix a problem is to remove the source of the problem?",
